---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Busuu Review: Learning Through Community" description="A social language learning app. Best for students who want feedback from native speakers on their writing and speaking exercises.">
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Review · Updated April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-1 mb-4">Busuu Review: Learning Through Community</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">A social language learning app. Best for students who want feedback from native speakers on their writing and speaking exercises.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-lg text-emerald-900">Our Rating</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-700">8.2/10</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-right">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Best for</p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-700">Community feedback</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">What is Busuu?</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Busuu combines traditional course materials with a unique social feature. When you complete a writing or speaking exercise, you can send it to the community for review. Native speakers will then provide corrections and tips. In return, you can correct exercises from people learning your native language.</p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Pricing</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Busuu has a free version, but the best features are locked behind the Premium subscription. Premium costs around $10 per month (billed annually) and includes offline mode, grammar lessons, and official certificates from McGraw Hill.</p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Pros</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600 mb-6">
    <li>Valuable feedback from a global community of native speakers</li>
    <li>High-quality, bite-sized lessons that are easy to finish</li>
    <li>Official certification for completing levels</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Cons</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600 mb-6">
    <li>The free version is very limited</li>
    <li>Community corrections can sometimes be inconsistent</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Verdict</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Busuu is one of the most effective language apps on the market because it forces you to produce the language, not just recognize it. The community feedback is a game-changer for solo learners.</p>
  <div class="bg-emerald-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-white mt-12">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Get corrected by native speakers</h3>
    <p class="mb-6">Join the Busuu community and start improving your English today.</p>
    <a href="https://www.busuu.com/" class="bg-white text-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">Visit Busuu</a>
  </div>
</article>
</Base>
